channel.title: Big Release
channel.description:
Well, i got bored off rsps now, i was hosting this server, on a 2gbr vps, it had up to 120 players + on weekends. i'm releasing this server because, i just do Not have time for it.
Features -
*Godwars.
*tomented demons.
*working curse's
*Barrows
*duel arena
*corp beast
*Warrior guild.
ok now to the pictures. -
Home. - [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/2mo9qwi.jpg[/img]
tormented demons. - [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/2h67hxg.jpg[/img]
Godwars.- [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/nz1xz5.jpg[/img]
warrior guild. - [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/a1n7ys.jpg[/img]
Corp. - [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/be6dl2.jpg[/img]
curse's.- [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/idatck.jpg[/img]
mini-game.- [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/2m28kyr.jpg[/img]
Hope you enjoy it, as much as i did.
source - mediafire.com/?f9im4917yqz2aok Client - mediafire.com/?6go3s1ub9oxdcl
